ass=title> Clarity Question</span><hr size=1> Hello, I have a 29 ench.  Does anyone know if clarity lasts longer as the ench level increases?   And if so by how much and at what levels.  I read someone's post that mentions the mana regen tick gets better at 35.  Is that the last level of increase in regen for the 29 clarity?  Would appreciate any knowledge you can pass along.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/urubicantdeluness.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rubicant DeLuness</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#330000>(5/2/02 6:46 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/twinr00bycloseup1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Clarity Question</span><hr size=1> Regen does not improve with the level of the chanter that casts clarity on you.  Clarity is always +8mana per tick, no more or less.  If you thought you were regenning more or less, it might have been because the chanter used gift of magic/insight/brilliance to increase your mana pool a bit, and it's also due to the fact that your innate mana regeneration increases with level.  A higher level chanter's buff *might* last a little longer, I've never checked that personally... <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87709>Master Rubicant D'Luness - Phantasmist</a><BR>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87724>Baroness Tryllian Sa'Sara - Disciple</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/umordy1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordy1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#330000>(5/3/02 9:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Clarity Question</span><hr size=1> Shadow, mana regen stats:<br>
<br>
Clarity - 7 per tick<br>
<br>
Clarity 2 - 11 per tick<br>
<br>
Kodiac's Endless Intellect - 14 per tick<br>
<br>
Gift series:<br>
<br>
Gift of Magic - no regen effect, adds 50 mana to base pool<br>
<br>
Gift of Insight - adds 1 mana per tick extra, 100 base mana to pool<br>
<br>
Gift of Brilliance - adds 2 mana per tick extra, 200 base mana to pool<br>
<br>
Gift series will not stack with KEI, KEI is an all in one buff adding mana regen, int/wis stats and more to base pool<br>
<br>
So a chanter with C2 and Gift of Brilliance can get 13 per tick and with Enlightenment near to KEI range.  However, KEI lasts 2 and a half hours, much better duration for mana ratio and stats are better.<br>
<br>
Hope this answers some questions.<br>
<br>
Mordy Lonesoul<br>
