<br>
Excellent post!  But to clarify the &quot;Clarity I&quot; data:<br>
<br>
Clarity - 4 to 7 mana per tick.  Formula is level/8 + 1.<br>
So from 29-31, it's 4/tick, 32-39 is 5/tick, 40-47 is 6/tick, 48+ is 7/tick.  And yes, I have tested this at the cutoff levels to prove it to myself.<br>
<br>
To the guy who thought Clarity provided 8/tick:  If you have Clarity up and no other mana regen buffs, you do regen mana at 8/tick (standing).  However, 1 of those is innate mana regen.  In other words, all casters regen mana at 1/tick while standing, with no other mana regen buffs.<br>
<br>
As to the duration of Clarity as the caster levels (the original question in the thread), it's a constant 27 minutes, regardless of caster's level.  Clarity 2 is similar (about 30 minutes).<br>
<br>
